# Ignore rules scoped to the lang/ composite build.
#
# Lives here (not at the repo root) so that lang/ stays self-contained
# in preparation for a future extraction into its own repository, and so
# that the top-level .gitignore only describes patterns that are truly
# repo-wide.

# IntelliJ Platform Gradle plugin cache.
# The intellij-platform-gradle-plugin downloads target IDE builds into
# `lang/.intellijPlatform/` (~4 GB) for buildPlugin / verifyPlugin /
# runIde / test. Outside `build/` on purpose: it is expensive to recreate
# and `gradlew clean` should not wipe it. The plugin manages its own
# lifecycle for this cache.
.intellijPlatform/

# Node module caches for any lang/ subpackage that uses Node tooling
# (currently lang/vscode-extension and the build-time tooling in
# lang/dsl). package-lock.json IS tracked at the subpackage level for
# reproducible installs; node_modules/ is the install output.
node_modules/
